comprehensive.user_template:
Analyze this traffic camera image comprehensively.

Respond ONLY with a valid JSON object in this exact format (no additional text):
{
  "weather": {
    "condition": "clear|cloudy|rainy|snowy|foggy|unknown",
    "visibility": "good|moderate|poor",
    "time_of_day": "day|night|dawn|dusk"
  },
  "road": {
    "type": "motorway|urban|rural|parking|intersection|unknown",
    "surface_condition": "dry|wet|icy|snowy|unknown",
    "lane_count": null
  },
  "traffic": {
    "density": "empty|light|moderate|heavy",
    "pedestrians_present": false,
    "cyclists_present": false
  },
  "risk": {
    "level": "low|medium|high|critical",
    "factors": []
  },
  "scene": {
    "type": "normal_traffic|construction|accident|special_event|other",
    "description": "Brief one-sentence description of the scene"
  },
  "confidence": 0.0
}

Replace placeholder values with your analysis. Set lane_count to an integer or null if unclear. Set confidence between 0.0 and 1.0 based on image clarity and your certainty.
